    "  The model performs **best on neutral sentiment** class with an F1-score of 0.77, driven by high recall(0.87). However, the relatively low precision(0.69) indicates that the model is biased towards predicting the neutral cases, frequently misclassifying both positive and negative tweets as neutral.\n",
